  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Universe is threatened by the mighty <strong>LORD CHAOSBRINGER</strong>, a primeval entity who has unleashed its chaotic hordes of elemental forces. The Universe needs <strong>YOU </strong>to defeat the forces of chaos and <strong>CLAIM THE TITLE</strong> of the <strong>MASTER BLASTER</strong>. Your journey will be difficult but fulfilling.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Blasting Action</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AIM </strong>and <strong>SHOOT </strong>your blasters against attacking hordes of elemental particles. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid, or take advantage of <strong>OBSTACLES </strong>and <strong>HAZARDS</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deal with unexpected air hockey-inspired <strong>PHYSICS </strong>behaviors and make them work for you, or they will not!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/6a8959d6457b9cd5768094628c93b0e2.poster.avif?t=1729431612\" width=640 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/6a8959d6457b9cd5768094628c93b0e2.webm?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/6a8959d6457b9cd5768094628c93b0e2.mp4?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Campaign Mode: Explore - Upgrade - Eliminate</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Galaxies to <strong>EXPLORE </strong> with <strong>50 Levels</strong> of gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-up by completing levels and earning powerful <strong>REWARDS</strong>. By becoming stronger you will <strong>UNLOCK</strong> new Star Systems.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make it to the<strong> FINAL battle</strong> against Lord Chaosbringer and <strong>save the universe</strong>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/bbd2540677fafec90c53dba0604c774c.poster.avif?t=1729431612\" width=640 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/bbd2540677fafec90c53dba0604c774c.webm?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/bbd2540677fafec90c53dba0604c774c.mp4?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survival Mode: Aim for the High-Score and dominate the leaderboard</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive <strong>INFINITE</strong> Waves of chaotic attacks for as long as you can. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each Run is UNIQUE,</strong> so only your skills and smart selection of power-ups can keep you in the game. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fallen <strong>CHAMPIONS </strong>will enter their <strong>NAME and SCORE</strong> in the Master Blaster’s <strong>STEAM LEADERBOARD</strong> (and earn bragging rights among their friends!)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/ca33a83e3122cf08afa8baca5abcb16a.poster.avif?t=1729431612\" width=640 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/ca33a83e3122cf08afa8baca5abcb16a.webm?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/ca33a83e3122cf08afa8baca5abcb16a.mp4?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade and Manage your Resources</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UPGRADE</strong> your Energy Capacitors to make your attacks even more effective and spectacular! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UPGRADE</strong> your Resilience to improve your resistance to enemy attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize <strong>Special Shooting TACTICS</strong> to Regenerate your Energy and Resilience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn meaningful <strong>REWARDS </strong>to reduce energy <strong>COSTS </strong>and enhance <strong>REGENERATION </strong>abilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/8a5967f260fcd16a123e5e75272c5ada.poster.avif?t=1729431612\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/8a5967f260fcd16a123e5e75272c5ada.webm?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/8a5967f260fcd16a123e5e75272c5ada.mp4?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Improve your Blastery!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn how to use <strong>COMBOS </strong>of Powerblasts, Collisions and Deflections to maximize the effect of your <strong>Shooting</strong>, while <strong>Regenerating </strong>your Energy and Resilience too! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharpen your reflexes in <strong>PRECISION</strong> challenges that will test your <strong>AIM and COORDINATION</strong> skills!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/1a5c33d523458d4e198befa0ae0ab56e.poster.avif?t=1729431612\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/1a5c33d523458d4e198befa0ae0ab56e.webm?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/1a5c33d523458d4e198befa0ae0ab56e.mp4?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tips and Tricks:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is <strong>optimized for CONTROLLERS</strong>. If your have one, use it! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for your <strong>ENERGY</strong> levels and<strong> prioritize to UPGRADE</strong> early on. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charge-up your shots (<strong>POWERBLASTING</strong>) to maximize Energy <strong>REGENERATION</strong> and <strong>SCORE</strong>! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STRATEGIZE</strong> your shots to amplify their effect versus energy cost. For example, you can regenerate your Resilience, get a power-up and do multiple kills with a single shot! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay calm and <strong>ENJOY Master Blaster!</strong> </p></li></ul>",
