" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/1a5c33d523458d4e198befa0ae0ab56e.poster.avif?t=1729431612\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/1a5c33d523458d4e198befa0ae0ab56e.webm?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713760/extras/1a5c33d523458d4e198befa0ae0ab56e.mp4?t=1729431612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tips and Tricks:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is <strong>optimized for CONTROLLERS</strong>. If your have one, use it! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for your <strong>ENERGY</strong> levels and<strong> prioritize to UPGRADE</strong> early on. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charge-up your shots (<strong>POWERBLASTING</strong>) to maximize Energy <strong>REGENERATION</strong> and <strong>SCORE</strong>! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STRATEGIZE</strong> your shots to amplify their effect versus energy cost. For example, you can regenerate your Resilience, get a power-up and do multiple kills with a single shot! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay calm and <strong>ENJOY Master Blaster!</strong> </p></li></ul>",
